data.description: Welcome home to the Spring Haven neighborhood!! This pool community is just what you have been looking for with easy access to I-20 and a corner lot.  This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is waiting for its new owners. A large foyer welcomes you as you are just a few steps away from open concept living. The master bedroom comfortably fits a king size bed and has a large walk-in closet in the large master bathroom. There is a patio through the sliding back doors where you can spend time with family. Seller is motivated and offering $2,000 towards buyer closing costs!!!! -Call me for a private tour of this beautiful home!!
